"1. Press the start button getting to the About phone. 2. Confirm the IMEI. 3. Get back to diagnostics tool and reply the test result."

"1. Launch the camera app with panorama mode. 2. Take a panorama picture from left to right then check picture quality. 3. Get back to diagnostics tool and reply the test result."
Can the portrait mode on this device work well?
"1. Launch the camera app with portrait mode. 2. Take a picture then check picture quality. 3. Get back to diagnostics tool and reply the test result."
Can the capture function on this device work well?
"1. Launch the front camera. 2. Take 1 time near shot(10-15cm) then check picture quality. 3. Get back to diagnostics tool and reply the test result."
Can the video function on this device work well?
"1. Launch the front camera. 2. Record a short video. 3. Get back to diagnostics tool and reply the test result."
Can the capture function on this device work well?
"1. Launch the rear camera. 2. Take a near shot (10-15cm) and a far shot (28cm and above) then check picture quality. 3. Get back to diagnostics tool and reply the test result."
